    General Stores in Mahim, Mumbai

    General Stores in Mahim, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Depending on the location of the store  whether in a rural village or an urban metropolis  the stock keeping units or pack sizes of the packaged goods may differ. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Mahim, Mumbai.
